General Orientation on Limited Face-to-Face Classes: Update

Due to unforeseen conflict in schedule and unavailability of some admin heads, the General Orientation for Limited Face-to-Face Classes has been moved. The rescheduled date is on January 31, 2022 at 1:00 PM. In the meantime, you may fill out this google form:bit.ly/3Asi2lkfor your pre-existing concerns and queries. So that they will be catered or entertained during the live orientation. The USG understands the possible frustration that this movement may bring. However, this will also serve as an avenue for the organizers and other people involved ample time for preparation to fully reach the objective of this event. Please be guided.

Posted on: 01/24/2022 | 01/24/2022 / ...

Apply now for a Full Time Instructor!

Status: Contract of Service (COS)Basic Salary: Php 31, 262.00/monthQualifications:1. Must be a graduate of any ITE Programs (BSCS/BSIS/BSIT) or other ITE-allied disciplines.2. Preferably holds at least a masters degree or units in ITE Graduate Programs/ITE-allied programs.3. Preferably with teaching experience. Fresh grads are also encourage to apply!4. Willing to teach ITE courses and perform other duties and task assigned.5. Flexible and can handle time-sensitive deliverables.Send your Application Letter, CV, TOR and other pertinent documents (pdf) address to:ANTHONY M. PENASO, Ph.D.University PresidentCaraga State UniversityAmpayon, Butuan CityE-mail us at: op@carsu.edu.phcc: ccis@carsu.edu.phSubject Line: CCIS FullTime Instructor 2022Apply now!

Best in Poblacion, Bayugan City

FOOD GARAGE

Healthy and affordable foods are in. All kind of moods are welcome! You can chill, sit, eat and relax. Eat & drink while you can.

Reservations Explore Menu

Food Garage

Our Delicious Story

A simple concept with a simple name.
That was the initial thoughts among a duo of friends in 2019 in a small kitchen in Bayugan that led to Food Garage's birth.

"Something exciting to eat and something nice to drink. Never ordinary, far from dull."

Thats how brief the Food Garage concept can be described and we hope that you - regardless of the extent to which this little adventure should come to - will continue to enjoy our combination of great craftsmanship, creativity and ambition that we have wrapped up in a simple surrounding free of table manners and waiting time.

item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: Flocer
item.content:encoded:
Know More

About Us.

Healthy and affordable foods are in. All kind of moods are welcome! You can chill, sit, eat and relax. Eat & drink while you can.

Our Resto.

A simple concept with a simple name.
That was the initial thoughts among a duo of friends in 2019 in a small kitchen in Bayugan that led to Food Garages birth.

Something exciting to eat and something nice to drink. Never ordinary, far from dull.

Thats how brief the Food Garage concept can be described and we hope that you regardless of the extent to which this little adventure should come to will continue to enjoy our combination of great craftsmanship, creativity and ambition that we have wrapped up in a simple surrounding free of table manners and waiting time.

Previous Next

A Few Words About Us

Serving Savory Meals, Snacks and Drinks Since 2019

As a destination, we try to manifests ourselves as more than a delicious bite. We wish to complete the dining experience within the spaces of our restaurants where raw industrial design portrays our setting for individuals coming together over bites and drinks.

View Menu

Free WiFi For Everyone

Ask for password to any staff

Smoked Stories

Our Menu.

Healthy and affordable foods are in. All kind of moods are welcome! You can chill, sit, eat and relax. Eat & drink while you can.

Best Meals and Snacks

Loved by Thousands

Something exciting to eat and something nice to drink. Never ordinary, far from dull.

Crispy Chicken

Chickenwith acrispycoating that's built to last!

95

The classic clubsandwichflavors get rolled up intortillas -- easy to eat

Mac Roll

55

Stuff springrollswithmac 'n' cheese and deep fry under golden

A hotdog bun with Holiday Cheesedog Footlong is encased snugly in a warm, freshly made tornado bread.

A classic Japanese sandwich: egg salad tucked between two fluffy slices of milk bread.

75

These homemadeBelgian wafflesare super crisp on the outside, light as a feather inside and so scrumptious!

Panini 'n Fries

145

A good combination where french fry with fluffy interior and crispy exterior and a smoked panini.
